snippet.title: Combat Beans: Total Mayhem - Teaser trailer
snippet.description:
Fast paced online shooter where you Battle other Beans for supremacy. Customize your bean and level up to unlock tons of unique cosmetics and dog tags! 

Join the discord
https://discord.gg/6vcRDyfVzr

Support the development by adding it to your steam wishlist
https://store.steampowered.com/app/1717080/Combat_Beans_Total_Mayhem/ 

Check out the latest Devlog here
https://store.steampowered.com/news/app/1717080/view/3507770137603574020

Coming early 2023!
